### -------------------- CONFIG TESTS --------------------

### Criar Config
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/configs
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "projectId": 4,
  "llmCredentialsId": {{llmCredentialId}},
  "modelName": "gpt-4.1-mini",
  "maxIter": 3,
  "checkPointInterval": 1,
  "additionalParams": {
    "llm.temperature": "0.2",
    "database.population_size": "3"
  }
}

### Ler Config por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/configs/{{configId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Ler todas as minhas Configs
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/configs/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Update Config
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/configs/{{configId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "modelName": "gemini-2.5-flash",
  "maxIter": 5,
  "checkPointInterval": 10,
  "additionalParams": {
    "llm.temperature": "0.6",
    "database.population_size": "20"
  }
}

### -------------------- PROJECT TESTS --------------------

### Criar Project sem configId,initial Program e evaluatorCode (deve aceitar null e criar projeto com valores default)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/projects
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Meu Primeiro Projeto",
  "description": "Um projeto de teste EvoLab",
  "configId": null,
  "initialProgram": null,
  "evaluatorCode": null
}

### Criar Project sem configId
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/projects
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Meu Primeiro Projeto",
  "description": "Um projeto de teste EvoLab",
  "configId": null,
  "initialProgram": "def solve(arr):\n    a = arr[:]\n    n = len(a)\n    for i in range(n):\n        swapped = False\n        for j in range(0, n - i - 1):\n            if a[j] > a[j + 1]:\n                a[j], a[j + 1] = a[j + 1], a[j]\n                swapped = True\n        if not swapped:\n            break\n    return a",
  "evaluatorCode": "import random\nimport time\n\ndef evaluate(candidate_code):\n    try:\n        ns = {}\n        exec(candidate_code, ns)\n        solve = ns.get(\"solve\")\n        if not callable(solve):\n            return {\"combined_score\": 0.0, \"correctness\": 0.0, \"speed\": 0.0}\n        tests = [[], [1], [2, 1], [3, 1, 2], [5, 5, 1, 3], list(range(20, 0, -1))]\n        random.seed(42)\n        for _ in range(6):\n            tests.append([random.randint(-100, 100) for _ in range(40)])\n        passed = 0\n        for t in tests:\n            out = solve(t[:])\n            if out == sorted(t):\n                passed += 1\n        correctness = passed / len(tests)\n        bench_input = [random.randint(-1000, 1000) for _ in range(250)]\n        t0 = time.perf_counter()\n        for _ in range(10):\n            solve(bench_input[:])\n        elapsed = time.perf_counter() - t0\n        speed = max(0.0, min(1.0, (0.05 - elapsed) / 0.05 + 1.0))\n        combined = 0.85 * correctness + 0.15 * speed\n        return {\"combined_score\": float(combined), \"correctness\": float(correctness), \"speed\": float(speed)}\n    except Exception:\n        return {\"combined_score\": 0.0, \"correctness\": 0.0, \"speed\": 0.0}"
}


### Ler todos os meus Projetos
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Ler todos os Projetos globais
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/projects
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Ler Projeto por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Update Project Details (Substituir parâmetros)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/4
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Projeto Atualizado",
  "description": "Nova descrição para o projeto",
  "initialProgram": "def hello():\n    print('hello mundo update')",
  "evaluatorCode": "def evaluate(candidate_code):\n    return {\"combined_score\": 1.0}",
  "configId": 1
}

### Iniciar Experimentacao de um Projeto
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/4/start
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Apagar um Projeto
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Atualizar Status do Projeto (Usado pelo Worker - normalmente sem Auth ou regras definidas)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/4/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "status": "CREATED"
}
